## Additional Legal Notice

This project is an **unofficial** integration with Quatt Home Battery. It is based on
reverse-engineered APIs and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or in any way officially
connected with Quatt or their official mobile application.

The Quatt mobile API is reverse-engineered and may change without notice. **Use at your own risk.**
There is **no official support** from Quatt for this integration.

For the official Quatt experience and support, please use the official Quatt mobile app or
visit https://www.quatt.io.
